{"tid":1760830,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"新時代消費地圖 neoguide.com","createTime":"2019-11-28T13:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:25:55.000Z","uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6fa2d3cbc2912698576a666c70d48a5d187ac8","tid":1760830,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://neoguide.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fneoguide.com&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=cb2a593b\" target=\"_blank\">neoguide.com</a><br />\n<br />\n我係搞手之一，我地成team人放左好多心機入去，做左差唔多四五個月，由google map轉去網頁，到而家每個星期developer都有新功能推出，令個地圖更加有用更加易用，希望大家可以支持下，入條link睇下，加埋webapp，follow ig/ fb。<br />\n<br />\n入去睇下，有咩comment放低，我今晚即覆。無comment既歡迎放低你用開個map，講下點解好用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊刻不容緩<br />\n驅逐共黨還我香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee66eb51c876039091d12d384047f63475ebce3a","tid":1760830,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">集會無嘢做？搭緊車好悶？嘆緊冷氣？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你哋一直想過嘅人權法過咗啦，仲唔快啲去多謝人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組會24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet like and reply <br />\n㩒入 ----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=7a96c4cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br /